[section#stmt.cont
    [:en] The [`:key continue] statement
    [:zh_CN] [`:key continue] 语句

[%  [:en] statement[![`continue]]
    [:zh_CN] 语句[![`continue]] ]
]

[para]
[:en] A [`:key continue] statement shall be enclosed by ([#stmt.pre]) an
[%[~iteration-statement]] [~iteration-statement] or an [~expansion-statement].
[`:key break] 语句应当被[%[~循环语句]][~循环语句]或[~展开语句]包围（[#stmt.pre]）。

[:en] If the innermost enclosing such statement [$X] is an [~iteration-statement] ([#stmt.iter]),
the [`:key continue] statement causes control to pass to the end of the [~statement]
or [~compound-statement] of [$X].
[:zh_CN] 如果其最内层外围的这种语句 [$X] 是一条[~循环语句]（[#stmt.iter]），
那么 [`:key continue] 语句导致控制转移到 [$X] 的[~语句]或[~复合语句]的末尾。

[:en] Otherwise, control passes to the end of the [~compound-statement]
of the current [$S_i] ([#stmt.expand]).
[:zh_CN] 否则，控制转移到当前 [$S_i] 的[~复合语句]的末尾（[#stmt.expand]）。
